            "link": "https://www.benzinga.com/news/politics/25/05/45692476/disturbed-by-trumps-actions-intelligence-employee-tried-to-share-state-secrets-with-foreign-government-to-support-values-the-us-stood-for-report",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-30 20:25:11",
