ury's surge past 5% makes investors wary of long-duration debt at a time when ballooning deficits threaten still-higher rates.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">Goldman Sachs has earned a growth score of 76.01% according to Benzinga Edge Stock Rankings. <a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/premium/ideas/benzinga-edge-2#:~:text=Turn%20Market%20Chaos,when%20markets%20rebound\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to see how it compares with other companies in the same space</a>.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><em>Photo Courtesy: Katiindies on Shutterstock.com</em></p><!--/$--><!--$--><div><div><div class=\"bz-campaign bz-campaign-bottom-45688909\" data-nosnippet=\"true\"><div class=\"sc-c014f608-0 kUPEDz skeleton min-h-[inherit] animate-pulse variant\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div></div><div class=\"flex sm:hidden flex-col\"><div class=\"sc-c014f608-0 kUPEDz skeleton min-h-[inherit] animate-pulse variant\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong>Read next: <a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/25/05/45687946/second-federal-judge-blocks-trumps-emergency-tariff-powers-hours-after-us-court-of-international-trade-ruling\" target=\"_blank\">Second Federal Judge Blocks Trump’s Emergency Tariff Powers, Hours After US Court Of International Trade Ruling</a></strong></p><!--/$--></div></div>",
